\u00ed tiene mi renuncia \n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|20}}\n | ShortSummary = Marco Mej\u00eda tries to intercept the communications of the Casillas. Ramiro tells Aurelio that the journalist who goes for him is Eugenia, Marco's wife.\n|LineColor=cdbd8c\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|El Se\u00f1or de los Cielos (season 1)\n |EpisodeNumber=  26\n |EpisodeNumber2= 26\n | Title= Tentaciones peligrosas\n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|21}}\n | ShortSummary = Matilde goes to bed with Heriberto. Chacorta tries to kill Eugenia. Marco Mej\u00eda and Chacorta were torn by gunfire.\n|LineColor=cdbd8c\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|El Se\u00f1or de los Cielos (season 1)\n |EpisodeNumber=  27\n |EpisodeNumber2= 27\n | Title= Todo por venganza\n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|22}}\n | ShortSummary = Do\u00f1a Alba delivers the documents of a new site for the school so that Rutila returns and returns to the studies.\n|LineColor=cdbd8c\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|El Se\u00f1or de los Cielos (season 1)\n |EpisodeNumber=  28\n |EpisodeNumber2= 28\n | Title= Secuestrada\n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|23}}\n | ShortSummary = Aurelio and Monica meet again. After the appointment of Ben\u00edtez, Doris proposes to Jim\u00e9nez that they organize a celebration for the high officials of the government.\n|LineColor=cdbd8c\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|El Se\u00f1or de los Cielos (season 1)\n |EpisodeNumber=  29\n |EpisodeNumber2= 29\n | Title= Qui\u00e9n es el infiltrado\n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|24}}\n | ShortSummary = Juan Villalobos tells Ximena that they have learned of the relationship of Heriberto and Matilde. Sonia accidentally hears the conversation between Ramiro and Irina and decides to intervene.\n|LineColor=cdbd8c\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|El Se\u00f1or de los Cielos (season 1)\n |EpisodeNumber=  30\n |EpisodeNumber2= 30\n | Title= Cu\u00eddate la espalda\n | OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|27}}\n | ShortSummary = El Cabo visits Aure