over, Maryland)|Capital Centre]], [[Landover, Maryland]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|9\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|9\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Javier Muniz\n|KO\n|1 (8), {{small|2:45}}\n|Mar 19, 1978\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[New Haven Coliseum|Veterans Memorial Coliseum]], [[New Haven, Connecticut]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|8\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|8\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Art McKnight\n|TKO\n|7 (8), {{small|1:52}}\n|Mar 1, 1978\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Hara Arena]], [[Dayton, Ohio]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|7\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|7\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Rocky Ramon\n|UD\n|8\n|Feb 4, 1978\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Civic Center, Baltimore, Maryland, U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|6\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|6\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|DOM}} Hector Diaz\n|KO\n|2 (8), {{small|2:20}}\n|Dec 17, 1977\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[D.C. Armory]], [[Washington, D.C.]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|5\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|5\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|MEX}} Augustin Estrada\n|KO\n|6 (8), {{small|1:54}}\n|Nov 5, 1977\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Caesars Palace]], [[Paradise, Nevada]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|4\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|4\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Frank Santore\n|{{abbr|KO|Knockout}}\n|5 (8), {{small|2:55}}\n|Sep 24, 1977\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Civic Center, Baltimore, Maryland, U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|3\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|3\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Vinnie DeBarros\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|3 (6), {{small|1:59}}\n|Jun 10, 1977\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Hartford Civic Center|Civic Center]], [[Hartford, Connecticut]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|2\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Willie Rodriguez\n|UD\n|6\n|May 14, 1977\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{sm